cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI. 

This paper is about a speech translation system, which involves both natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also mentions the use of hybrid-HMM models for speech recognition, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SD (Sound). Additionally, the use of neural machine translation models falls under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning). Finally, the post-processing module may fall under the sub-category of cs.SI (Signal Processing).
